nodes.name: WSTCrowdsale

attributes.name: WSTCrowdsale

devdoc.details: Contract accept ETH and mint new WSTToken for the ETH sender. The Crowdsale has some features: CappedCrowdsale: Max ETH cap the Crowdsale accept. TimedCrowdsale: Crowdsale starts on openingTime and closes on closingTime. MintedCrowdsale: The Crowdsale mints new token via the WSTToken contract.

buyTokens(address).details: low level token purchase ***DO NOT OVERRIDE*** This function has a non-reentrancy guard, so it shouldn't be called by another `nonReentrant` function.

capReached().details: Checks whether the cap has been reached.

constructor.details: Contract constructor accepts parameter and initialize the crowdsale.

params._cap: Max cap in ETH for Crowdsale.
params._wallet: Wallet address where ETH will be sent.

hasClosed().details: Checks whether the period in which the crowdsale is open has already elapsed.

isOpen().return: true if the crowdsale is open, false otherwise.

rate().return: the number of token units a buyer gets per wei.

wallet().return: the address where funds are collected.

devdoc.title: WST Token Crowdsale contract.
